                "tag": "li",
                "text": "RESUME"
            },
            {
                "tag": "p",
                "text": "RESUME"
            },
            {
                "tag": "li",
                "text": "More"
            },
            {
                "tag": "p",
                "text": "More"
            },
            {
                "tag": "h1",
                "text": "ABOUTEVAN SWOPE"
            },
            {
                "tag": "p",
                "text": "I am a Creative Director who has made 8 original brands (and their design guidelines), expanded the output of small brands' media campaigns by 5x, and worked in every format of media from producing on documentaries, to print and digital ads, email and social, even scoring music for contemporary dance, and robotics."
            },
            {
                "tag": "h2",
                "text": "EVERY BRAND HAS A VOICE"
            },
            {
                "tag": "p",
                "text": "Learning who your customers are and how to talk to them, or even talk like them, is key to creating a likeable digital persona. Let's work together to find out who we're talking to and how we can sound like the voice of authority, a friend, or an intriguing mystery to be solved."
            },
            {
                "tag": "h2",
                "text": "Visual first"
            },
            {
                "tag": "p",
                "text": "The best campaigns start off with great visuals, and no industry is without a need for powerful, evocative, and relatable imagery. This can start with cohesive product photography, and be as large as multimedia ad campaigns to capture audiences on social, TV, and even radio or streaming audio services."
            },
            {
                "tag": "h2",
                "text": "KNOW trends"
            },
            {
                "tag": "p",
                "text": "There's a world of data out there. Where do you start? I like to start with search term clusters and competitor analysis. What else do people search for when they search for your products? What kinds of videos do people watch on social channels? Trends help you find where the attention already is."
            },
            {
                "tag": "h2",
                "text": "Form a team"
            },
            {
                "tag": "p",
                "text": "Maybe you've never touched an ad platform, or worked with a voice actor before. Don't worry! I can help find the right talent and tools for the job. Communications can be scaled up based on success when we've found a resonant message."
            },
            {
                "tag": "h2",
                "text": "Okay but who is Evan"
            },
            {
                "tag": "p",
                "text": "Alright, alright. In my off time, I like to dabble in hobbies like home improvement in my condo, stand-up comedy, and drag. I lived in Portland, OR, and Tri-Cities, WA before moving to Seattle to attend University of Washington Seattle. I've been here ever since."
            },
            {
                "tag": "h1",
                "text": "FOLLOW"
            },
            {
                "tag": "p",
                "text": "Copyright © 2026 Evan Swope Digital LLC"
            }
        ],
